                <h3>Coconut Rice</h3>
                <p>Coconut Rice is a fragrant and flavorful South Indian dish made by cooking rice with freshly grated coconut and tempered with mustard seeds, curry leaves, green chilies, and urad dal. Sometimes, cashews or peanuts are also added for extra crunch and flavor. Coconut Rice is often served as a main course or as a side dish with curries or chutneys.
</p>
