            <div class="card-content">
                <h3>Fish Curry</h3>
                <p>Fish Curry is a spicy and tangy South Indian curry made with fish cooked in a flavorful gravy made from coconut, tamarind, and a blend of spices such as coriander, cumin, turmeric, and chili powder. The fish is typically marinated with spices before being cooked in the gravy until tender. Fish Curry is usually served with rice or dosa.
</p>
                <p>Price: &#8377;500</p>
                <span style="background-color: #ff0000; color: white; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 4px;">Non-Veg</span>    
            </div>
        </div>
        <br>
