                <h3>Vegetable Korma</h3>
                <p>Vegetable Kurma is a creamy and aromatic South Indian curry made with mixed vegetables cooked in a rich and flavorful coconut-based gravy. The gravy is made from coconut, cashews, poppy seeds, and spices like cinnamon, cardamom, cloves, and fennel seeds. The vegetables are cooked in this gravy until tender, resulting in a delicious and wholesome dish. Vegetable Kurma is often served with rice, roti, or dosa.
</p>
                <p>Price: &#8377;400</p>
